OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FInspectors found mould     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbefore man's death -       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Finquest                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Council inspectors found damp, mould   
OL,6, and leaks at the home of a man who     
OL,7, later died but these complaints were   
OL,8, not followed up, an inquest has heard. 
OL,10,FLuke Brooks' parents have previously   
OL,11,Fclaimed mould in their Oldham home     
OL,12,Fcaused his death in October 2022.      
OL,14,FJoanne Collier, from the environmental 
OL,15,Fhealth team at Oldham Council, told    
OL,16,FRochdale Coroner's Court there were    
OL,17,F"missed opportunities".                
OL,19,FThe inquest heard various defects were 
OL,20,Ffound over a four-year period.         
